and other line-shape parameters. The correlation between Dicke narrowing and speed-dependent
broadening is studied. The measured parameters are compared to a series of spectroscopic
databases and previously published results.},
keywords = {Carbon dioxide, Cavity ring-down spectroscopy, Line intensity, Transition
frequency, Pressure broadening coefficient, Pressure shifting coefficient},
