Network for Trace gases by Airline), and HIPPO (HIAPER Pole-to-Pole Observations),
yielding typical biases of -1.7 ppm in the 5-13 km range. The standard error of
these biases in this vertical range is 0.4 ppm. The multi-year ACE-FTS data set
